eld and below investment grade securities market european specialty lending logineuropean specialty lending   providing private capital for middle market european companieseuropean businesses have traditionally relied on bank funding but regulations are changing the way many companies approach their financial needs our european team utilizes their many longstanding relationships across the private equity advisor and corporate communities to source lending opportunities our access to longterm capital and ability to invest across the debt capital structure allow us to provide the bespoke financing solutions needed by private equity sponsors and corporates our objective is to provide investors with attractive riskadjusted returns and current income while seeking preservation of principal investmentan experienced investor in european private debt crescent’s investment strategy extends across the european continent crescent’s european senior investment professionals average over  years of relative lending experience direct lending logindirect lending   senior secured lending to the us middle market since  the direct lending team has developed a reputation as a responsive and trusted source of capital for us private equitybacked companies we provide a wide range of senior financing alternatives including revolving credit facilities term loans delayed draw term loans second lien loans and unitranche facilities to support our private equity clients’ platform acquisitions portfolio company addons recapitalizations and refinancings our objective is to provide investors with high current income with an emphasis on capital preservation and attractive risk adjusted returns   with current capital in excess of  billion crescent direct lending is well positioned to support our private equitybacked middlemarket clients led by senior investment professionals who average over  years of lending experience the crescent direct lending team has supported private equity firms across a wide