and pension and profit sharing plans it manages client specific portfolios and investment funds for its clients the firm invests in alternative credit markets it diversifies its investments across public and private credit m crescent capital group lp is an employee owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles state or municipal government entities high net worth individuals corporations private funds special purpose or single investor funds separate accounts and structured products trusts estates foundations endowments and other charitable organizations family offices and institutional investors including insurance companies and pension and profit sharing plans it manages client specific portfolios and investment funds for its clients the firm invests in alternative credit markets it diversifies its investments across public and private credit markets including senior bank loans high yield debt mezzanine debt distressed debt securities us and european senior loans us high yield bonds and senior secured floating rate debt obligations it employs technical and fundamental analysis with bottom up and topdown analysis approach to make its investments the firm combines external research with inhouse research for its investments it also specializes in special situation investments in distressed middle market companies the firm primarily invests in the fulcrum debt tranche of underfollowed companies its mezzanine investments focus on leveraged acquisitions laterstage growth financings buyouts recapitalizations and refinancings and are in the form of junior debt capital and private debt securities with equity participation the firm also provides between  million to  million of senior secured debt to private united states lowermiddlemarket companies with annual ebitda of  million to  million and enterprise values in excess of  million its target investments include cashflow based senior secured debt senior term b debt and senior unitranche debt crescent capital group lp was founded in may  and is based in los angeles california with additional offices in new york new york and boston massachusetts detailed description  santa monica boulevardsuite los angeles ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwcrescentcapcom key executives for crescent capital group lp ms irina rudnitsky fund manager mr jeanmarc chapus managing partner age  mr mark louis attanasio jd managing partner and cofounder age  mr gerhard lombard chief financial officer age  ms christine k vanden beukel managing director of european credit and head of crescents european specialty lending strategy compensation as of fiscal year  crescent capital group lp key developments crescent capital group lp presents at institutional and alternative lending conference new york  jun  pm jun   crescent capital group lp presents at institutional and alternative lending conference new york  jun  pm venue new york new york united states speakers john s bowman managing director of direct lending crescent capital group lp presents at the th annual milken institute global conference may  pm apr   crescent capital group lp presents at the th annual milken institute global conference may  pm venue the beverly hilton  wilshire boulevard beverly hills ca  california united states speakers steven koehler senior vice president of capital markets crescent capital group announces hiring of kenneth mcray and glynell bradley as senior vice presidents in investor relations apr   crescent capital group lp announced that kenneth mcray and glynell bradley have joined the company as senior vice presidents in investor relations mr mcray will focus on expanding the firm’s business development efforts across institutional investors and mr bradley will further enhance crescent capital’s relationships with consultants and gatekeepers mr mcray brings more than  years of experience in the financial industry he joins crescent capital from pinebridge investments wher