supplier of durable pest control products and a portfolio company of wind point partners pl systems used the capital in large part for the addon acquisition of the environmental care unit of group de ceuster a manufacturer and distributer of chemical pest control solutions with operations in belgium the netherlands and france the crossborder european transaction fits within crescent’s longstanding underwriting standards and its commitment to providing access to capital for middle market companies “we are pleased to have completed this transaction with pl in support of its acquisition of gdc enviro which when combined will become a leading manufacturer and supplier of pest control products in western europe” said christine vanden beukel managing director and head of crescent’s european specialty lending strategy “this transaction is representative of the increased interest we are seeing by sponsors and management teams to access capital through unitranche financings provided by established alternative asset managers” about crescent capital group crescent capital group lp an secregistered investment adviser is headquartered in los angeles with offices in boston london and new york with approximately  investment professionals and  employees the firm invests at all levels of the capital structure with a significant focus on below investment grade credit through strategies that invest in senior bank loans high yield debt mezzanine debt distressed debt and other private debt securities as of september   crescent capital group managed approximately  billion in assets with a relatively equal split between marketable securities and privately originated debt investments about pl systems pl is a market leading global supplier of pest control products the company has a comprehensive portfolio of predominantly durable pest control solutions and possesses inhouse product development capabilities the company’s customer base comprises over  pcos and municipalities with end users spanning  countries pl is headquartered in harrogate uk about the environmental care unit of group de ceuster the environmental care unit is a market leading manufacturer and distributor of pest control products with operations in belgium the netherlands and france the business’s product portfolio comprises chemical pest solutions eg insecticides for which it has significant rd and manufacturing capabilities its brands are highly recognized in their markets and it also offers private label products and manufacturingformulation services about wind point partners wind point partners is a private equity investment firm that partners with top caliber ceos to acquire middle market businesses where we can establish a clear path to value creation since their founding in  wind point has raised over  billion in commitments additional information about wind point is available at wwwwindpointpartnerscom print email share via email separate multiple email addresses with commas share send me a copy email preview to from subject look at this story on pe hub crescent capital invests in wind point partnersbacked pl systems crescent capital has made an undisclosed investment in pl systems a ukbased pest control products provider pl systems is a a portfolio company of wind point partners continue reading on pe hub writes do you want exclusive news and analysis about private equity deals fundraising topquartile managers and more get your free trial to buyouts or subscribe now sign up to our newsletter receive updates from our pe hub wire and top stories of the week newsletters first name last name email address us edition daily canada edition weekly we will not send you spam and we dont share your email address with rd parties i accept the terms and conditions you are now subscribed to the pehub wire and top stories of the week newsletters buyouts insiderargosy group llc produces several free newsletters that are sent directly to the email you provide at registration namely pe hub wire 